<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ t.name_zh }} · 每日三理</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
{% import "_card.html.j2" as card %}

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="wrap header-inner">
    <div class="brand"><h1>每日三理</h1><span class="en">Theoria</span></div>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="../index.html">今日</a>
      <a href="../archive.html" class="active">歷史</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="wrap">

  <section class="hero">
    <a class="back-link" href="../archive.html">← 回理論庫</a>
    <div class="date">{{ status_label }}</div>
    <div class="lead">回頭重讀這則理論的完整三天弧。{% if unlocked_day < 3 %}（這則正在進行中，目前到第 {{ unlocked_day }} 天，其餘分頁解鎖後可讀。）{% else %}三天都已解鎖，可自由切換。{% endif %}</div>
  </section>

  {{ card.card(t, unlocked_day) }}

</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap">每日三理 · Theoria{% if generated_at %} — 更新於 {{ generated_at }}{% endif %}</div>
</footer>

<script src="../assets/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
